        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1200314342" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4752891889953691767">I adore Neruda&apos;s poetry. The only reason that I am giving 4 stars and not 5, is because the &quot;woman as a doll&quot; imagery that he seems fond of using put me off every time I came across it...</span>
  <span id="freeText4752891889953691767" style="display:none">I adore Neruda's poetry. The only reason that I am giving 4 stars and not 5, is because the "woman as a doll" imagery that he seems fond of using put me off every time I came across it...</span>
