<div id="review_3808572317" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3808572317" />
    <a title="Luís" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/117399210-lu-s"><img alt="Luís" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1620236159p2/117399210.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3808572317?book_show_action=true">Jan 31, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Luís" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Luís" href="/user/show/117399210-lu-s">Luís</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback " href="/book/show/19377871-vinte-poemas-de-amor-e-uma-can-o-desesperada">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/117399210-lu-s?shelf=favorites">favorites</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/117399210-lu-s?shelf=poetry">poetry</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/117399210-lu-s?shelf=classics">classics</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/117399210-lu-s?shelf=latin-american">latin-american</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/117399210-lu-s?shelf=romance">romance</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3808572317" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15359079570848683717">It is true that when it comes to an author so popular, so admired, something extraordinary expected, and therefore it spoils this effect of discovery. It was my first Neruda; a bilingual collection (where I also had fun reading the original version) made up of three small clusters of different shapes. Elementary writing, but which reaches grandeur, where the woman is at the centre; all types of women and metaphors. Neruda has managed to express himself around such familiar topics as love and wom</span>
  <span id="freeText15359079570848683717" style="display:none">It is true that when it comes to an author so popular, so admired, something extraordinary expected, and therefore it spoils this effect of discovery. It was my first Neruda; a bilingual collection (where I also had fun reading the original version) made up of three small clusters of different shapes. Elementary writing, but which reaches grandeur, where the woman is at the centre; all types of women and metaphors. Neruda has managed to express himself around such familiar topics as love and women without falling into bad taste and without missteps as if he is walking acrobatically on the blade of a knife. I have fond memories of this reading; I enjoyed some metaphors and some puns.</span>
  <a data-text-id="15359079570848683717" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


